==English==

===Verb===
'''[[squirrel]] [[away]]'''

#{{idiom}} To [[stash]] or [[hide]]; to [[hoard]], [[collect]], [[save]], or [[accumulate]]; to create a [[reserve]], [[stash]], or [[hoard]] of some [[supply]].  
#:''He had bits of string, cans of nails and lots of other useful tidbits '''squirreled away''' throughout his garage.''